Package: CQRM
Type: Package
Title: Composite Quantile Regression Models for Count-Based Differential Expression
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2026-06-23
Authors@R: person("Zhangchi", "Xu", email = "xzc0907@umd.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides four permutation-calibrated MinP differential expression tests
    for non-coding RNA (ncRNA) count data based on composite quantile regression
    score statistics. The methods aggregate rank-score statistics across multiple
    quantile subsets and calibrate p-values via a multivariate normal null
    distribution. Functions: CQRM (all 2^K-1 non-empty subsets), CQRM.best
    (single-quantile MinP), CQRM.region (contiguous-window MinP), and CQRM.approx
    (fast no-jitter approximation using a single rq.wfit call per quantile).
